#labels components, help
#useful informations about some components


= JTextField that only allows numerically inputs =

You can use the JNumberOnyTextField.java class in the de.htwds.rembrandt.components package.

= Set the text color of disabled JTextFields =

You can use the setDisabledTextColor(Color c) method.
For example:
{{{
	this.txtStateProvinz = new JTextField();
	this.txtStateProvinz.setDisabledTextColor(getForeground());
	this.textAreaBusinessAdress = new JTextArea();
	this.textAreaNotices.setDisabledTextColor(getForeground());
}}}